1. *ćemo* odraditi zadatak (We will do the task)
2. Oni *će* nam pomoći (They will help us)
3. Oni će biti tu do sutra (They will be here until tomorrow)
4. Ja *ću* odmah otići (I will leave right away)
5. Da li *ćemo* dobiti dozvolu? (Will we get the permission?)
6. Oni *će* danas stići (They will arrive today)
7. *ćemo* nastaviti dalje (We will continue further)
8. Oni *će* nam ponuditi pomoć (They will offer us help)
9. Mi *ćemo* se vratiti za dva dana (We will come back in two days)
10. Oni *će* biti tu sutra (They will be here tomorrow)